
Quick steps to build FastJetClustering:
---------------------------------------

    - FastJetClustering depends on the following packages: LCIO GEAR Marlin ROOT FastJet, CMake and CMakeModules.
        
        if you have access to /afs/desy.de/ then you will find all this packages under:

            /afs/desy.de/project/ilcsoft/sw/i386_gcc34_sl4/   # SL4 32bit
            /afs/desy.de/project/ilcsoft/sw/i386_gcc41_sl5/   # SL5 32bit
            /afs/desy.de/project/ilcsoft/sw/x86_64_gcc41_sl5/ # SL5 64bit


        if you do NOT have acces to /afs/desy.de/ or you do not have an SL4/SL5 machine the easiest
            way is to use ilcinstall (http://ilcsoft.desy.de/portal/software_packages/ilcinstall/).
            Please use an ilcinstall version >= v01-10.
    

            Set the ilcinstall installation path in releases/v01-10/release-versions.py
            Comment out any tools other than the FastJetClustering dependencies in both configuration
                files: release-base.cfg and release-ilcsoft.cfg


            And launch:
            ilcsoft-install releases/v01-10/release-base.cfg   # to install the core tools
            ilcsoft-install releases/v01-10/release-ilcsoft.cfg   # to install the remaining tools

